text: Wilhelm Kaufmann (born 17 February 1872, date of death unknown) was a German gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1872 births Category:Year of death missing Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
